      <caption>
        <p>Processing time and memory usage of micRocounter across 15 representative genomes. In each panel the x axis represents genome size of the benchmark genomes in Mb. A) Comparison of execution time for micRocounter and Palfinder on benchmark genome set. B) Execution time for micRocounter on benchmark genome sets with time on a log scale. C) Peak memory usage running micRocounter on benchmark genomes.</p>
